XPATH 

Attributes:
 id,class, name value,type,etc., 
 
 To take xpath right click on the element --> inspect and dom page will appear
 

Locating elements with attributes:
//tagname[@attribute='values']
e.g:- //input[@value='Append']

//*[@attribute='values']

Locating elements with texts:
//tagname[text()='Actual text']
e.g:-//label[text()='Clcik on the text']

Locating elements with partial texts:
//tagname[contains(text(),'partial text')]
e.g:-//label[contains(text(),'Facebook helps')]

Locating element from multiple attribute
//tagname[@attribute='values'][@attribute2='value2']..[@attributeN='valueN']
e.g:-//input[@type='button'][@value='Search']

Locating element with starting text:
//tagname[starts-with(text(),'starting text')]
e.g:-//label[starts-with(text(),'Facebook')]

Locating elements with dynamic attributes:
//tagname[starts-with(@attributeName,'fixed value']
eg:-//input[starts-with(@id,'entityid')]
//tagname[contains(attributeName,'part ofthe value')]
eg:-//input[contains(id,'entityid')]
